# Master Gitignore for Banking Application (Full Stack)

# --- Backend (Spring Boot) ---
**/target/
**/.mvn/wrapper/maven-wrapper.jar
**/.idea/
**/*.iml
**/*.log
**/*.http

# --- Local Project Data (CRITICAL: Do not push these) ---
**/data/
**/reports/

# --- Frontend (React/Vite) ---
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/dist-ssr/
**/*.local
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# --- IDE & OS ---
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
*.sw?
src/test/resources/application-test.properties